column1: Do you currently have a mental health disorder?
column2: Have you been diagnosed with a mental health condition by a medical professional?
column3: Have you ever sought treatment for a mental health issue from a mental health professional?
column4: Do you feel that being identified as a person with a mental health issue would hurt your career?
column10: Has your employer ever formally discussed mental health
column11: Is your anonymity protected if you choose to take advantage of mental health treatment resources provided by your employer?
column12: Would you feel comfortable discussing a mental health disorder with your coworkers?
column13: Would you feel comfortable discussing a mental health disorder with your direct supervisor(s)?
column14: Do you believe your productivity is ever affected by a mental health issue?
column15: If yes, what percentage of your work time (time performing primary or secondary job functions) is affected by a mental health issue?
